{"tid":2237522,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★聶德權：現職公務員拒宣誓 不擁護基本法和不效忠特區「是很嚴重的事」，完全不能容許","createTime":"2020-10-10T10:57:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-10T14:35:08.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"a82c07c5d6228b6fa45dc15317ed170fb80a313c","tid":2237522,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T10:57:39.000Z","msg":"若現職公務員拒絕簽署聲明或宣誓，聶德權說會先研究其法律理據，亦會了解箇中原因，但他指這些行為表示了一種態度，「是否不擁護基本法？不效忠特別行政區？」被問到當局會如何處理違反誓言的公務員，他強調須嚴肅認真地看待誓言；他又說，<span class=\"xx-large\">不擁護基本法和不效忠特區「是很嚴重的事」，完全不能容許</span>，「牽涉到該人是否堅守一國原則、接受一國兩制」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20201010/s00002/1602266695214/%E8%81%B6%E5%BE%B7%E6%AC%8A-%E7%8F%BE%E8%81%B7%E5%85%AC%E5%8B%99%E5%93%A1%E6%8B%92%E5%AE%A3%E8%AA%93%E6%88%96%E7%A4%99%E5%8D%87%E9%81%B7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20201010%2Fs00002%2F1602266695214%2F%25E8%2581%25B6%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E6%25AC%258A-%25E7%258F%25BE%25E8%2581%25B7%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258B%2599%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%258B%2592%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E8%25AA%2593%25E6%2588%2596%25E7%25A4%2599%25E5%258D%2587%25E9%2581%25B7&d=qh2qPVBUtyR5HqmPKg%2BIDCwbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=8447c341\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20201010%2Fs00002%2F1602266695214%2F%25E8%2581%25B6%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E6%25AC%258A-%25E7%258F%25BE%25E8%2581%25B7%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258B%2599%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%258B%2592%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E8%25AA%2593%25E6%2588%2596%25E7%25A4%2599%25E5%258D%2587%25E9%2581%25B7&h=a4f768a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20201010/s00002/1602266695214/%E8%81%B6%E5%BE%B7%E6%AC%8A-%E7%8F%BE%E8%81%B7%E5%85%AC%E5%8B%99%E5%93%A1%E6%8B%92%E5%AE%A3%E8%AA%93%E6%88%96%E7%A4%99%E5%8D%87%E9%81%B7</a>"},{"pid":"0c4d5ed26edfa6213089a0a1e199cf754f9c154